name: Ganqing | Genshin Impact (Keqing + Ganyu)
description:
Just new model train with keqing and ganyu dataset. So it mean possible to add 2 character in same image in same time.

Recommended model

  • Pastel-Mix [Stylized Anime Model] ->

  • Counterfeit-V2.5 ->

  • 9527 ->

  • Cetus-Mix (Highly recommended) ->

The main trigger word is keqing \(genshin impact\)and ganyu \(genshin impact\). Weight should be between 0.6 - 0.75 for the 1.0 version.

Anyway implementation is similar with this 2 lora -> Keqing , Ganyu

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update WebUI or Redownload it -> Tutorial

  • Copy the Lora file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • In Prompt add <lora:{lora_filename}:{weight}>

  • replace {lora_filename} with lora_filename

  • replace {weight} with weight you want
